n|-\n| rowspan=\"6\" |2009\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" |''[[The Killing Room]]''\n|[[Jonathan Liebesman]]\n|Third collaboration with Jonathan Liebesman<br> Nominated- [[International Film Music Critics Association|IFMCA Award for Best Original Score for a Horror/Thriller Film]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''[[Dragonball Evolution]]''\n|[[James Wong (producer)|James Wong]]\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''[[Fast & Furious (2009 film)|Fast & Furious]]''\n|[[Justin Lin]]\n| Fourth collaboration with Justin Lin\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" |''[[The Final Destination]]''\n| [[David R. Ellis]]\n| Themes by [[Shirley Walker]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''[[Middle Men (film)|Middle Men]]''\n|[[George Gallo]]\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''[[Law Abiding Citizen]]''\n| [[F. Gary Gray]]\n| First collaboration with F. Gary Gray\n|-\n|2010\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" |''[[The Expendables (2010 film)|The Expendables]]''\n|[[Sylvester Stallone]]\n| rowspan=\"3\" |[[BMI Film Music Award]]\n|-Second collaboration with Sylvester Stallone\n| rowspan=\"3\" |2011\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" |''[[Battle: Los Angeles]]''\n|[[Jonathan Liebesman]]\n|-Third collaboration with Jonathan Liebesman\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" |''[[Fast Five]]''\n|[[Justin Lin]]\n|-Third Collaboration with Justin Lin\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''[[Final Destination 5]]''\n|[[Steven Quale]]\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" | 2012\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''[[John Dies at the End (film)|John Dies at the End]]''\n| [[Don Coscarelli]]\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''[[Columbus Circle (film)|Columbus Circle]]''\n| [[George Gallo]]\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''[[Brake (film)|Brake]]''\n| Gabe Torres\n| {{