lt]]\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2016\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" |''[[Criminal (2016 film)|Criminal]]''\n|[[Ariel Vromen]]\n| Composed with Keith Power\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''[[Now You See Me 2]]''\n| [[Jon M. Chu]]\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" | 2017\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''[[XXX: Return of Xander Cage]]''\n| D. J. Caruso\n| Composed with Robert Lydecker    \n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''[[Power Rangers (film)|''Power Rangers'']]''\n| [[Dean Israelite]]\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''[[The Fate of the Furious]]''\n| [[F. Gary Gray]]\n| Second Collaboration with F. Gary Gray\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''[[The Mummy (2017 film)|''The Mummy'']]''\n| [[Alex Kurtzman]]\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n|2018\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" |''[[Crazy Rich Asians (film)|''Crazy Rich Asians'']]''\n|[[Jon M. Chu]]\n|Nominated- [[International Film Music Critics Association|IFMCA Award for Best Original Score for a Comedy Film]]\n|-\n| rowspan=\"6\" |2019\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''[[Escape Room (film)|Escape Room]]''\n| [[Adam Robitel]]\n|Composed with John Carey\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''[[What Men Want (2019 film)|What Men Want]]''\n|[[Adam Shankman]]\n|{{N/A}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''[[Five Feet Apart]]''\n|[[Justin Baldoni]]\n|Composed with Breton Vivian\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''[[Ready or Not (2019 film)|Ready or Not]]''\n|[[Matt Bettinelli-Olpin]]<br />[[Tyler Gillett]]\n|{{N/A}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''[[Rambo: Last Blood]]''\n| [[Adrian Grunberg]]\n| Themes by [[Jerry Goldsmith]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''[[Charlie's Angels (2019 film)|Charlie's Angels]]''\n| [[Elizabeth Banks]]\n| Themes by [[Jack Elliott (composer)|Jack Elliott]] and [[Allyn Ferguson]] \n|-\n| 2020\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''[[Those Who Wish Me Dead]]''\n| [[Taylor Sheridan]]\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n| TBA \n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''[[Clouds (upcoming film)|Clouds]]''\n| [[Justin Baldoni]]\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n|}\n\n=== Short films ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Director\n! Notes\n|-\n|2001\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" |''Offside''\n|[[Leanna Creel]]\n| \n|-\n|2003\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" |''Last Stand''\n| Gabe Torres\n| \n|-\n| 2005\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" |''Clair obscur''\n| Benjamin Charles-Lemaire\n| \n|-\n|2011\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" |''Tattoo''\n|[[Bill Paxton]]\n| \n|-\n|2014\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" |''[[Marvel One-Shot: All Hail the King|All Hail the King]]''\n|[[Drew Pearce]]\n| Composed with [[Mike Post]]\n|}\n\n===Television film===<!-- Television films belong here according to WikiProject: Actors and Filmmakers -->\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Director\n! Notes\n|-\n| 1998\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''Final Justice''\n| [[Tommy Lee Wallace]]\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n| 1999\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''[[Sirens (1999 film)|Sirens]]''\n| [[John Sacret Young]]\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n|2000\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" |''[[Trapped in a Purple Haze]]''\n|[[Eric Laneuville]]\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n|2001\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" |''[[Jane Doe (2001 film)|Jane Doe]]''\n|Kevin Alyn Elders\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n|2002\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" |''[[Last Call (2002 film)|Last Call]]''\n|[[Henry Bromell]]\n|Nominated- [[Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Music Composition for a Limited Series, Movie, or Special|Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Music Composition for a Limited Series]]\n|-\n|2003\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\"