 Bettinelli-Olpin]]<br />[[Tyler Gillett]]\n|{{N/A}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''[[Rambo: Last Blood]]''\n| [[Adrian Grunberg]]\n| Themes by [[Jerry Goldsmith]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''[[Charlie's Angels (2019 film)|Charlie's Angels]]''\n| [[Elizabeth Banks]]\n| Themes by [[Jack Elliott (composer)|Jack Elliott]] and [[Allyn Ferguson]] \n|-\n| 2020\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''[[Those Who Wish Me Dead]]''\n| [[Taylor Sheridan]]\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n| TBA \n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''[[Clouds (upcoming film)|Clouds]]''\n| [[Justin Baldoni]]\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n|}\n\n=== Short films ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Director\n! Notes\n|-\n|2001\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" |''Offside''\n|[[Leanna Creel]]\n| \n|-\n|2003\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" |''Last Stand''\n| Gabe Torres\n| \n|-\n| 2005\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" |''Clair obscur''\n| Benjamin Charles-Lemaire\n| \n|-\n|2011\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" |''Tattoo''\n|[[Bill Paxton]]\n| \n|-\n|2014\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" |''[[Marvel One-Shot: All Hail the King|All Hail the King]]''\n|[[Drew Pearce]]\n| Composed with [[Mike Post]]\n|}\n\n===Television film===<!-- Television films belong here according to WikiProject: Actors and Filmmakers -->\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Director\n! Notes\n|-\n| 1998\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''Final Justice''\n| [[Tommy Lee Wallace]]\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n| 1999\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''[[Sirens (1999 film)|Sirens]]''\n| [[John Sacret Young]]\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n|2000\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" |''[[Trapped in a Purple Haze]]''\n|[[Eric Laneuville]]\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n|2001\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" |''[[Jane Doe (2001 film)|Jane Doe]]''\n|Kevin Alyn Elders\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n|2002\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" |''[[Last Call (2002 film)|Last Call]]''\n|[[Henry Bromell]]\n|Nominated- [[Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Music Composition for a Limited Series, Movie, or Special|Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Music Composition for a Limited Series]]\n|-\n|2003\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" |''[[Thoughtcrimes]]''\n|[[Breck Eisner]]\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n| 2005\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''[[Painkiller Jane (film)|Painkiller Jane]]''\n| [[Sanford Bookstaver]]\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n|2014\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''[[Marvel Studios: Assembling a Universe]]''\n| {{N/A}}\n| Television special\n|}\n\n===Television series===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Notes\n|-\n|1997\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''[[Jenny (TV series)|Jenny]]''\n|17 episodes\n|-\n|1998\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''[[Living in Captivity]]''\n|8 episodes\n|-\n|2000\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''[[Level 9 (TV series)|Level 9]]''\n|13 episodes\n|-\n|2001\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''[[The Education of Max Bickford]]''\n|22 episodes\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2003\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''[[Frank Herbert's Children of Dune]]''\n|3 episodes\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''[[Star Trek: Enterprise]]''\n| Episodes \"[[Canamar]]\" and \"[[Regeneration (Star Trek: Enterprise)|Regeneration]]\"\n|-\n|2007\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''[[Fear Itself (TV series)|Fear Itself]]''\n|Episode: \"[[The Sacrifice (Fear Itself)|The Sacrifice]]\"\n|-\n|2010\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''[[Hawaii Five-0 (2010 TV series)|Hawaii Five-0]]''\n|84 episodes\n|-\n|2010\u201313\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''[[Transformers: Prime]]''\n|66 episodes\nNominated- [[Daytime Emmy Award|Daytime Emmy Award for Outs